name: Diletta Leotta
description:
Giulia Diletta Leotta; born 16 August 1991, is an Italian television presenter from Catania, Sicily. Leotta currently presents the Serie A broadcasts for DAZN since the 2018–2019 season.

If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon!

Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

This is my first job: a textual inversion to use Diletta Leotta. This is my first job, every feedback is welcome! I used 30 public images of her. To use it,

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder

  • Then simply add dilleotta to your prompt and enjoy!

  • Keep the Samples around 20, CFG between 7 and 8, but feel free to experiment!

Have fun!
